The Secretary for the Department of National Emergency Services has the following functions in relation to Disaster Risk Management:
* coordinating the following services:
	* Nauru Rescue and Fire Services;
	* Nauru Ambulance Services;
	* Nauru Life Guard Services;
	* Nauru Meteorology Services;
	* coordinating the maintenance of the National Disaster Risk
	* facilitating the implementation of the National Disaster Risk
	* preparing, reviewing and testing the National Disaster Risk

